data.description: Delightful ranch. Owner pride shows throughout this cozy bungalow. Newer Interior paint, newer kitchen cabinets. New furnace & electric updated in 2019. New roof in 2022 New stove, refrigerator & carpet in 2023!  4th (possible 5th bedroom) in unfinished basement. Family/rec room (currently a Billiard room!)in basement. Pool  Table & Accessories included with full price offer!  Large back yard, trex deck, with awning, shed, front & back sprinklers, perfect for summer entertaining. UNC, Shopping, Parks, Restaurants, & Schools conveniently close.
